Race.SpecificTitle: Parishwide Home Rule Charter -- Amends Art. III, Sec. A, Sub. 4 & Sec. B, Sub. 1 - PC
Race.FullText: Shall the West Feliciana Parish Home Rule Charter be amended to change the term limits provisions for the Parish President from two terms to three terms and confirm the regular election cycle to coincide with the regular Louisiana gubernatorial elections?
